name: City of Life
description:
Here life is flourished, awareness is multiplied and love is an abundant commodity. Every child grows up learning to think freely, care for other forms of life and develop sophisticated  methods of connecting to beings without bodies. 

It's an utmost necessity for children and adults alike to utilize brain power and mind capacity to design marvels of engineering and science to be tested and built by intelligent machines.

Digital Painting
2048x1536 Pixels

2016
